en_198978_0	Underworld member “Choota”, the mastermind behind the underworld group “Ninja”, has been arrested in Dematagoda during a raid carried out by the Colombo crimes Division last evening.
en_198978_1	It is reported that the 31-year-old individual is a resident of Ihala Biyanwila – Kadawatha.
en_198978_2	Police have also seized an automatic firearm possessed by the suspect.
en_198978_3	Further investigations have revealed that Athukoraala Kankaa-namge Sandun Priyadarshana alias Choota is a close accomplice of underworld kingpin Angoda Lokka who is currently in hiding overseas.
en_198978_4	It has also been revealed that another accomplice of him identified as Thuwan, is already in prison.
en_198978_5	In response to an enquiry made by our news team, a senior official at the Colombo Crimes Division stated that investigations have been launched into the suspect on multiple fronts.
